          <li><strong>Broker regulator:</strong> FCAA (Financial and Consumer Affairs Authority)</li>
          <li><strong>Key economy:</strong> Agriculture, potash, oil & gas, uranium</li>
          <li><strong>Avg home price (2026):</strong> ~$330,000–$380,000</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg p-5" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card)">
